@c ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@node hypot, math
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <math.h>

double hypot(double x, double y);
@end example

@subheading Return Value

The length of a hypotenuse of a right triangle whose shorter sides are
@var{x} and @var{y}.  In other words, the distance between (0,0) and
(@var{x},@var{y}).
